      <title>拜登將宣布與美光達成高達 61.4 億美元晶片補助的初步協議</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/biden-announce-preliminary-deal-with-micron-up-614-bln-chip-grants-2024-04-25/</link>
