      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/stmicro-cuts-fy-revenue-outlook-slowing-car-demand-bites-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[歐洲晶片製造商意法半導體週四下調了全年銷售指引，這是最新一家因汽車製造商需求疲軟以及筆記型電腦和手機公司訂單進一步下降而苦苦掙扎的半導體公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/stmicro-cuts-fy-revenue-outlook-slowing-car-demand-bites-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 05:17:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
